    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/79dc509e68c4f98739a60b20fc0b3d07.avif?t=1754929818\" width=616 height=266 /></span><br><strong>Devotion, betrayal, vengeance, and redemption.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/d71d3faf49943f706e90d21e60362647.poster.avif?t=1754929818\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/d71d3faf49943f706e90d21e60362647.webm?t=1754929818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/d71d3faf49943f706e90d21e60362647.mp4?t=1754929818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Uncover the dark secrets of &quot;The Order&quot; to achieve divine redemption.<br>A Souls-like game with an isometric view.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/38cc281aa321fc2423f230767dc4ff4a.avif?t=1754929818\" width=616 height=266 /></span><br>Help Cedric find redemption. Use your melee or ranged attacks, increase your magical powers, and solve puzzles to access certain areas. Immerse yourself in the underworld and defeat the evil one.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/5fe084bcb58e8d7e7d5b74d63c10c687.avif?t=1754929818\" width=616 height=194 /></span><br>Explore the world of Ironholt, delve into the depths of Sombracave, or face the defenders of the various fortresses condemned by the evil one.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/71cb76e7a5b01e1136442afb391931fb.avif?t=1754929818\" width=616 height=194 /></span><br>Choose your attack style wisely—melee, ranged, or magic—each enemy has its weaknesses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/bfa9eeac66e2a8c67c3f9ce88f6823b2.avif?t=1754929818\" width=616 height=266 /></span><br>Investigate your enemies, seek information about their pacts with the evil one and the curse they bear. Gather all the treatises to gain the power to confront the lord of evil.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/0d391b51236b314622e992d36fa70903.avif?t=1754929818\" width=616 height=266 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/3611d9ee2976203a5fffb5298aa6ac4f.poster.avif?t=1754929818\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/3611d9ee2976203a5fffb5298aa6ac4f.webm?t=1754929818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095630/extras/3611d9ee2976203a5fffb5298aa6ac4f.mp4?t=1754929818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Buy, sell, or try your luck at gambling to earn enough money to get potions or magic cards—any help in Ironholt is little enough.",
